skins.name: Default
skins.secIdle1Text: Commander, don't just stand there, come play with me!
skins.secIdle2Text: Hahaha, look! Spence's reactions are so hilarious!
skins.secIdle3Text: Since I don't know when I'll do something wrong, I'll just go ahead and apologize now.
skins.secTouchText: I know what it is you really want to touch, weirdo!
skins.secSpecialTouchText: Hoho? You wanna touch me there again?
